item.description: Dancing at the Princeton Station, the band plays 9-1. We usually try to gather tables along the back wall under the windows. No reservations here so everyone jumps in and helps out. Always a good time and fun dancing to FOTF. Come out and meet some new friends and enjoy the evening.
